final_poem:
Beneath the vast expanse of azure skies,  
The mighty sea whispers secrets to those who listen in its tide;   
Waves dance with grace on sandy shores,    
While sunlight dapples through their fluid doors, creating ripples and hues that adorn. Deep beneath the surface lies an underwater world of life teeming—a realm unseen by those above but profound in its silent roar;  
The ocean’ enduring rhythm echoes eternity's heartbeat within our earthly sphere, reminding us to respect and preserve every precious droplet.
